00:05:56.980 --> 00:06:00.980
But we find first this evening, despise not prophesying.

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:02.859
So we have to understand,

00:06:02.859 --> 00:06:04.920
as we look at this verse of scripture,

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:07.820
what is it that Paul is referring to?

00:06:07.820 --> 00:06:10.279
